Welcome to PythonRadio

A commandline python frontend to mplayer with a list of popular internet radios.

Please feel free to add your favorite internet stations to the list.

Installation of PythonRadio requires mplayer to be installed on your system
for example "apt-get install mplayer" will work for debian based systems.

Ensure you have pythonradio in your $PATH usally located on a sane system in your .bashrc

PATH="$PATH:/home/davro/workspace/project-pythonradio/bin"


